description: In his inaugural address to the newly formed cabinet, Egypt’s Prime Minister Mostafa Madbouly underscored the importance of economic stabilisation and the outcomes of the National Dialogue. title: Egypt PM prioritises economic stabilisation, National Dialogue in first Cabinet address

description: Talaat Moustafa Group Holding (TMG) has achieved a significant milestone, securing a staggering EGP 340bn ($7.1bn) in sales as of July 8, 2024.
